stateDiagram-v2
  [*] --> Idle

  Idle --> Recording: manual start\npush-to-talk pressed\ntoggle pressed
  Recording --> Transcribing: manual stop\npush-to-talk released\ntoggle pressed
  Transcribing --> Idle: transcription complete

  Recording --> Idle: recoverable runtime error
  Transcribing --> Idle: recoverable runtime error

  Idle --> Error: non-recoverable runtime error
  Error --> Idle: next successful action\nor permission recovery

  state Recording {
    [*] --> Capturing
    Capturing --> Capturing: audio snapshot + interim inference\n(1200ms cadence)
  }

  state Transcribing {
    [*] --> FullInference
    FullInference --> OutputActions: post-process + clipboard + paste safety checks
    OutputActions --> [*]
  }
